---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Glossary
description: Definitions of common property inspection terms, abbreviations, and industry jargon.
---
<section class="section-block">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">Reference</span>
    <h1>Glossary</h1>
    <p>Key terms and definitions used in property inspection.</p>
    <dl class="glossary-list">
      {%- for term in collections.glossary %}
      <div class="glossary-list__item" id="{{ term.data.title | slugify }}">
        <dt>{{ term.data.title }}</dt>
        <dd>{{ term.templateContent | safe }}</dd>
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>
